                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 136.) I was present when the in<lb></lb>spector read the charge to the prisoner at the station—the prosecutor was pre<lb></lb>sent—the prisoner said, "I do not think he will appear against me."</p>
